Text.val: Create report for download in batch [pi-_OpdrachtID<>0]

ExpSyntax.val: Trim({0,34})&' and '&'A.DATE_IN BETWEEN TO_DATE('&ASCIIChr(39)&DStr({0,13},'YYYY/MM/DD')&' 00:00:00'&ASCIIChr(39)&','&ASCIIChr(39)&'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS'&ASCIIChr(39)&')'&' AND TO_DATE('&ASCIIChr(39)&DStr({0,15},'YYYY/MM/DD')&' 23:59:59'&ASCIIChr(39)&','&ASCIIChr(39)&'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS'&ASCIIChr(39)&')'

SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT ID, PPR_ID, RE_REKENING, MUTATION_ID, AMOUNT, DATE_IN, IF_ID, STATUS
FROM (
SELECT A.ID, A.PPR_ID, E.RE_REKENING, A.MUTATION_ID, A.AMOUNT, A.DATE_IN, A.IF_ID, A.STATUS
FROM :2 A, --WM_ORDER :3 B, --ORIN_STATES :4 C, --EXT_IDENTIFICATION_POSS_VW :5 D, --INVESTMENT_FLOWS :6 E, --REKENINGEN :8 F, --PRODUCTEN_PER_RELATIE :9 G -- CLIENTEN
WHERE :1
AND (B.STATE_ID=A.STATUS AND C.PPR_ID=A.PPR_ID AND D.ID(+) =A.IF_ID AND E.RE_ID=A.DEPOT_ID AND A.PPR_ID=F.PPR_ID AND F.PPR_RELATIENUMMER=G.CL_NUMMER)
UNION
SELECT A.ID, A.PPR_ID, E.RE_REKENING, A.MUTATION_ID, A.AMOUNT, A.DATE_IN, A.IF_ID, A.STATUS
FROM :7 A, --HIST_WM_ORDER :3 B, --ORIN_STATES :4 C, --EXT_IDENTIFICATION_POSS_VW :5 D, --INVESTMENT_FLOWS :6 E, --REKENINGEN :8 F, --PRODUCTEN_PER_RELATIE :9 G --CLIENTEN
WHERE :1
AND (B.STATE_ID=A.STATUS AND C.PPR_ID=A.PPR_ID AND D.ID(+) =A.IF_ID AND E.RE_ID=A.DEPOT_ID AND A.PPR_ID=F.PPR_ID AND F.PPR_RELATIENUMMER=G.CL_NUMMER) )
ORDER BY ID DESC
